Module es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step

The TextProc processing step API, including unprocessed document types, step interfaces and abstract classes, and process definition document handling logic. This module is of interest for those willing to extend TextProc with more processing capabilities.
Author:
Alejandro González García
